OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower supply issue takes BBC
OL,4,CTwo's live snooker off the air
OL,5,
OL,6,FTonight's live coverage of the World
OL,7,FSnooker Championships on BBC Two was
OL,8,Fdisrupted for a time due to power
OL,9,Fsupply issues.
OL,11,FPictures and sound froze at around
OL,12,F7.50pm. After about 40 seconds, the
OL,13,Fstandard BBC Two breakdown graphic
OL,14,Fappeared.
OL,16,FAfter a short time we had what appeared
OL,17,Fto be a live apology from an announcer.
OL,19,FOver four-and-a-half minutes of silence
OL,20,Ffollowed before another announcer
OL,21,Fprovided a further apology before
OL,22,Flinking into a short filler programme.
OL,23,EPub: 30-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,149,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14802
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F148A1781467885
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower supply issue takes BBC
OL,4,CTwo's live snooker off the air
OL,5,
OL,6,FAfter ten minutes we rejoined the live
OL,7,Fcoverage, with the fourth frame between
OL,8,FMark Allen and Wu Yize just underway.
OL,10,FPresenter Hazel Irvine immediately
OL,11,Fapologised for the disruption,
OL,12,Fexplaining that it was due to power
OL,13,Fissues.
OL,15,FHazel explained during the next
OL,16,Finterval that there was a big "crash,
OL,17,Fbang, wallop" in the stadium which led
OL,18,Fto a power surge which is believed to
OL,19,Fhave caused the power to fail.
OL,23,EPub: 30-Apr-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,149,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14803
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F148A1781467885
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/3
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GBLOOPERSCPower supply issue takes BBC
OL,4,CTwo's live snooker off the air
OL,5,
OL,6,FOn return to the live action, the
OL,7,Fon-screen scoreboard was briefly
OL,8,Funavailable. There was also a loss of
OL,9,Fsound for a few minutes before normal
OL,10,Fservice was fully resumed.
OL,12,FBBC Two Northern Ireland and BBC Two
OL,13,FWales remained with network BBC Two for
OL,14,Fthe entire breakdown and filler
OL,15,Fprogramme.
